messages.text: Hey – is this Sophia?
who is this?
Do I have the right number?
yes?
It’s Mark. So so sorry I missed our date last night
oooooh. hi mark
that’s okay, no worries
I wanted to apologize in person but by the time I got there, you’d left
well, it had been almost two hours…
that’s long enough to wait for a blind date lol
Well, yeah, I don’t blame you
I had the craziest night ever but I didn’t mean to stand you up
haha i see
I wanted to text you but unfortunately I didn’t have access to my phone
I just didn’t want you to think I was the type of guy to leave people hanging
yeah, sarah told me you’re a good guy
don’t worry about it
Awesome, thanks
Just fyi I was really looking forwards to meeting you
Sarah told me you’re really cool and definitely my type
And I haven’t realllly been having great luck on my own in that department
I know right now I look like a jerk but I promise I’m not that bad
Is there any chance you would be down to meet up again?
It could be a sort of ‘make up’ blind date
hmmm, depends
On what?
what exactly happened?
what was so ‘crazy’ that it kept you from meeting up with me?
Oh. It’s a looong story that I would rather tell you in person
if you didn’t want to go on a blind date, it’s okay to just say so
i was nervous about it too, lol
Nah that wasn’t it
to be honest with you, the last blind date i went on went horribly wrong
so your ‘craziest night ever’ had better be good
Well what happened to you?
where do i even begin
this guy was the most uncoordinated person i’ve ever seen
first he tripped me when he tried to pull my chair out for me
then he knocked over our wine and stained my dress
and then he accidentally cut himself with his steak knife
we literally had to go to the emergency room
Wow that’s awful
Hasn’t the man ever heard of band-aids?
just wait. it gets worse
in the emergency room, this lady gets wheeled past us right?
and she’s screaming bloody murder because she’s in labor
she’s basically about to give birth right in front of us
Well that’s definitely romantic
turns out, this lady is the guy’s EX-GIRLFRIEND
he didn’t know she was pregnant
our sad excuse of a date was his introduction to the entire fact
Wtf
What are the chances
JUST WAIT
it gets worse
How???
you won’t even believe it
How could it get more bizarre then that
so the lady starts screaming ‘CHAD CHAD IT’S YOU’
lol Chad
i know.
anyway, she’s like freaking out and he’s all
‘BECKY WHAT THE HECK IS HAPPENING’
and she goes ‘IT’S YOURS’
NO
LOL
OMG
Are you messing with me?? This cannot be real
i WISH i was messing with you
so he follows her into the emergency room
they proceed to have the baby together
and what with me being a yoga teacher, they make me stay
to help her keep her breathing steady or whatever
basically i was there until the kid arrived at 3 am
they named him sophocles after me
the person who magically brought them back together
Okay, I have to call your bluff on that one
There’s no WAY they named him Sophocles
okay okay you caught me
they named him eugene
but i thought sophocles would be more appropriate
considering that they never would’ve run into each other if not for me
so basically, go on a blind date with me and you will instantly become a father
still interested?
Wow…
I gotta be honest, I don’t know if I’m ready for fatherhood just yet
That’s a lot of diapers
do you want kids in general?
Well, yeah, a while down the road though
better avoid me like the plague then lol
Nah, sounds more like you’re an instrument of destiny
You brought them together for Eugene
yeah yeah
okay so be real with me
why did you skip our date last night?
you don’t seem like the type
I promise you I’m not
I actually was never absent from school, all the way from kindergarten through high school
Very unlike me to miss something
that is actually very impressive
so???
So I was on my way to meet you
And as I was leaving my apartment building, I locked myself out by accident
laaaaame
booooo
Wait! The story gets better I promise
I call my landlord, and he doesn’t pick up, I knock, no answer
So I try to break in.
oh god
I start trying to climb up the side of my building and force my way into my window that’s cracked a bit open
And this lady walking down the street sees me and starts screaming at me
Soon a crowd forms and people are live-tweeting the whole thing
Because by this time, I’m stuck. Did I mention I’m deathly afraid of heights?
oh noooo!!! hahaha
and then what happened???
Meet me in person and you can know the rest.
come on!!! what a tease
i told you what happened in my story
Life isn’t fair Sophia
Otherwise I would’ve made our date last night, which I can already tell would’ve been amazing.
Based on how great you are over text
…okay
Okay?
okay, we can go out again (but really, go out for the first time)
but on one condition
What?
i get to show up whenever i want
and give you a taste of your own medicine
Fair enough
Definitely seems like you’re worth waiting for
flattery will get you everywhere
how’s tonight at 8? same place?
Sounds good. See you tonight when you finally get there at 10.
I’ll bring the diapers just in case I suddenly discover I’m a father.
haha don’t forget the band-aids either! can’t wait, see you soon
Can’t wait.
